'''''Lost in the Desert'''''<ref>https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/lost-in-the-desert</ref> ku '''''ikubitiro''''' yasohotse nka Dirkie, ni filime yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo yo mu 1969 yanditswe<ref>https://birthmoviesdeath.com/2016/01/13/everybodys-into-weirdness-lost-in-the-desert-1969</ref>, yakozwe kandi iyobowe na Jamie Uys ku izina rya Jamie Hayes<ref>https://makeminecriterion.wordpress.com/2020/04/26/dirkie-lost-in-the-desert-jamie-uys-1970/</ref>. Yafashwe amashusho muri Techniscope na Technicolor<ref>https://www.fragrantica.com/perfume/BAU/Lost-In-The-Desert-50264.html</ref> . Uys ubwe akina nka  Anton De Vries, umucuranzi wa piyano w'igitaramo cy'umuhungu we Dirkie wimyaka 8 <ref>http://www.mimosafilms.co.za/Archive/Film/71/dirkie-aka-lost-in-the-desert-</ref>. Dirkie akinishwa n'umuhungu wa Uys Wynand Uys, uzwi nka Dirkie Hayes<ref>https://www.radiotimes.com/movie-guide/b-wj7awz/lost-in-the-desert/</ref>. Umugambi wahujwe nyuma yimyaka ibiri na "Walkabout" yatsinze cyane<ref>https://www.bfi.org.uk/lists/10-great-films-set-desert</ref> <ref>https://bestsimilar.com/movies/51271-dirkie-lost-in-the-desert</ref>.

== Telugu remake ==
Isubiramo ryamamaye cyane ryakozwe mu rurimi rwa Telugu<ref>https://www.ebay.com/p/1862420984</ref>, ururimi rwo mu majyepfo [[Ubuhinde|y’Ubuhinde]], mu 1972, ku izina rya ''Papam Pasivadu''  hamwe n’impinduka nkeya zahinduwe mu nkuru kugira ngo zihuze n'abari aho<ref>https://gaana.com/song/lost-in-the-desert-2</ref>.

